verbose_text: The results confirm the low complementation potential of the human GnTI gene in plants, as previously shown by Gomez and Chrispeels, however, in their case the complementation potential of human GnTI gene in Arabidopsis was not directly related to expression and activity of the wild-type Arabidopsis GnTI gene.
evidence: expression and activity of the wild-type Arabidopsis GnTI gene
